	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;184&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;443px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;forward bias = short ckt.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;实际应用&#34;&gt;实际应用&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;普通电路&#34;&gt;普通电路&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;651&#34;
	height=&#34;628&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/3_hu58888682caf793bc6cce35eb5aa73fbf_83736_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/3_hu58888682caf793bc6cce35eb5aa73fbf_83736_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;103&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;248px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;正向&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;加限流电阻，防止二极管被烧坏&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;反向&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;不能超过&lt;strong&gt;击穿电压&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;整流器&#34;&gt;整流器&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;定义&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AC$\longrightarrow$DC,理想状况下没有损失&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol start=&#34;2&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;图示&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;694&#34;
	height=&#34;364&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/4_huc8c98a50e4786ea55266f190d33aa06f_63785_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/4_huc8c98a50e4786ea55266f190d33aa06f_63785_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;190&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;457px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;分段线性法&#34;&gt;分段线性法&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;二极管的终端特性&#34;&gt;二极管的终端特性&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
i = I_S (e^{V/V_T}-1) \\\
\\ I_S: 给定温度，给定二极管的一个常数 \\\
\\ V_T:热电压，室温下(20C^\circ),V_T = 25.3(mV) \approx 25mV
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;正向偏置&#34;&gt;正向偏置&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V \gg V_T \\\
\\ i = I_Se^{V/V_T} \Longrightarrow V = V_T \ ln\Big(\frac{i}{i_S}\Big)
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;反向偏置&#34;&gt;反向偏置&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
v \lt 0 \Longrightarrow i\approx -I_S
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;击穿区域&#34;&gt;击穿区域&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V \lt V_{ZK} \\\
\\ I_{max} \lt P_{max} / V_Z
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;图示&#34;&gt;图示&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/5.png&#34;
	width=&#34;919&#34;
	height=&#34;591&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/5_hu62171d0168de2dbefb33c9f8d2360768_87215_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/5_hu62171d0168de2dbefb33c9f8d2360768_87215_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
