&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;二极管正向属性模型化&#34;&gt;二极管正向属性模型化&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;指数二极管模型&#34;&gt;指数二极管模型&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;代数分析&#34;&gt;代数分析&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/6.png&#34;
	width=&#34;375&#34;
	height=&#34;208&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/6_hu926c6c1d67da850b398fbd47b61cbbb8_19261_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/6_hu926c6c1d67da850b398fbd47b61cbbb8_19261_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;180&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;432px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V_{DD} = V_D + V_R \\\
\\ \begin{align}
I_D= I_S e^{V_D/V_T} \\
I_D = \frac{V_{DD}-V_D}{R}
\end{align} \\\
\\ From (1)(2)
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;图像分析法&#34;&gt;图像分析法&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/7.png&#34;
	width=&#34;741&#34;
	height=&#34;439&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/7_hu34714c725c98219f96ec3069a88f32b0_82711_480x0_resize_box_3.png 480w, https://downeyflyfan.com/p/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1/7_hu34714c725c98219f96ec3069a88f32b0_82711_1024x0_resize_box_3.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;168&#34;
